sources.title: Western Movie | The Courtship (1960) Bonanza
sources.description:
Hoss falls prey to the wiles of a beautiful woman with a gambling addiction and refuses to believe she's only interested in his money in spite of Adam's proof to the contrary.
 
Director: James P. Yarbrough
Writer: Richard Morgan 
Stars: Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker, Michael Landon 
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
